{
  "stem": "13079.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Dachau.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Dachau, you got to remember, was located just 17 kilometers north and west of Munich.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we-- the Third Army was there in Munich, the rear echelon.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, first of all, I utilized the reports of the war-crimes teams that had been coming in.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, actually, Seventh Army was the army that liberated Dachau.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they had a war-crimes team there under the command of Colonel Chavez, whose brother was Senator Chavez from New Mexico.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Colonel Chavez and his  men filed a magnificent report, setting forth the different facets of the operations of the Dachau camp.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And using their reports as a guide, we started investigating and preparing for the trial of the Dachau concentration camp case.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First thing we had to do was decide on a charge.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What was it that-- how could you frame this charge?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were a lot of problems in that connection.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because these camps had been going on since 1933.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, we didn't have any jurisdiction until the war-- till we ended the war and after December the 7th.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And these camps were being tried as war crimes, their operation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And war crimes, of course, are defined as those that are in violations of the laws and usages of war.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the United States was participating after December the 7th.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the limits time-wise, so far as the time was concerned, was December 7th, 1941.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's when the United States had jurisdiction, because that's when they came into the war.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were a combatant from that time on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, we would go through the documents that had been accumulated there in Munich and tried to sift out and see what conduct was available to bring to the attention of the court.",
      "word_count": 33
    }
  ],
